@node "nws3" "Atéo News"

@{fg shine} Atéo November news@{fg text}

NOVEMBER 1998

Sorry! We miss the October monthly letter!!!

Web:

New downlaod section, with 'Aminet' like readme.

AtéoBus Software:

A new StatAteoBus version is available in download section, this is the
version 3.4 which is more stable than the 2.50. This new version is needed
by ateoser.device and ateopar.device.

AtéoBus expansion boards:

All the serial and parallel boards are available to end users.

Here they are:

- AtéoPar I: 1 x ECP parallel port
- AtéoSer I: 1 x RS232C serial (up to 462Kb)
- AtéoSer II: 2 x RS232C serial (up to 462Kb)
- AtéoSer II mini: 2 x RS232C serial (up to 462Kb) with 9 pin connectors
- AtéoIO I: 1 x ECP parallel port and 2 x RS232C serial port (up to 462Kb)


We still are designing others boards:

- Ethernet board:
We currently work on an Ethernet with 10BaseT (BNC) and RJ45 connection.
This
 board should be available quickly.

- Sound card:
A several channel (32) sound card including FM synthesizer, mixer, several
input ouput, sample table and cache memory is on the way.

- Pixel 64 Scan doubler
